    {
      "id": "77c2786a-cc24-4f79-980d-bbf46595c36c",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Knowledge Tracing involves estimating the knowledge state of a student and using that knowledge state to understand whether they wil get a question right or wrong. However, an underlooked aspect of KT is temporal aspects and forgetting behavior. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "77c2786a-cc24-4f79-980d-bbf46595c36c",
        "parent": {
