    {
      "id": "d9e29302-0a8e-4759-8768-2045e10fb7e4",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "To address this limitation, authors propse a new-transformer based KT model that incorporates the aspects of time and forgetting behavior in order to create a more accurate estimation of a learner’s knowledge state. When benchmarking the results using the EdNet KT3 dataset, the authors find their proposed architecture outperforms all baseline models significantly both in terms of accuracy and AUC.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "d9e29302-0a8e-4759-8768-2045e10fb7e4",
        "parent": {
